text: Alisha Donga (born 12 April 2002) is a Solomon Islands women's footballer who plays as a midfielder for the Solomon Warriors. ==Career== Donga made her international debut for the Solomon Islands on 15 July 2019, at the 2019 Pacific Games match against the Cook Islands.
